    DEF INPUT PARAMETER wInitSortColNavn AS CHAR NO-UNDO. 
    DEF VAR wW            AS WIDGET        NO-UNDO.
    DEF VAR wCount        AS INTE   INIT 1 NO-UNDO.
    DEF VAR wLookUp       AS INTE          NO-UNDO.
    DEF VAR wNySearchCols AS CHAR          NO-UNDO.
